|---|-------|------|--------|
| 1 | FE scope | `resources/js/services/property_liability/burglary/scope.js` | Add code to `ENDORSEMENT_CODES` |
| 2 | FE perms | `resources/js/permissions.js` | `'<code>':'<NAME>_ENDORSEMENT'` in `PER_ENDORSEMENT_BY_PRO_CODE` |
