### Edit ‚Üí submit contract (0191 pattern)

| Step | Endpoint | Payload |
|------|----------|---------|
| Persist Policy Info | `POST /pl/endorsements/{id}` (`_method=PATCH`) | Full `UpdateRequest` (insured, period, channel, clauses, limits, ‚Ä¶) |
| Persist premium / endt info | `PATCH ‚Ä¶/save-info` | `EndorsementInfoRequest` |
| Final submit | `PATCH ‚Ä¶/submit` | `{ product_code }` only (Detail page) |

Do **not** POST partial endt-only fields to the heavy `UpdateRequest` endpoint (422). Persist endt meta via `/save-info` (`saveEndorsementPremium` / `EndorsementTab.vue`) or fold into full Policy Info update. Carry `endorsement_option`, refund, and file fields from existing endt when patching info.

